<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span><span class="c1">"لا يصح"</span> انتهى.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span><span class="c1">"المحلى"</span> <span class="c2">(٥/٨٤)</span> .<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
